                                                                <p>We have five key goals for the Youth & Government program.</p>
                                                                <p>1.	Develop a strong sense of community (inter-delegate/delegation relationships) and realism (strict imitation of the structures and processes of the Maryland)</p>
                                                                <p>2.	Increase the opportunities, encouragement and support for young people to grow as leaders of their communities through a model legislature and court; values based leadership development; and direct service.</p>
